      Constructors in bytecode with parameters of type ComparableType 
      Constructor and Description
      EQ(ComparableType type)
      Constructs a bytecode that checks if the top two elements of the stack are the same.
      IF_CMPEQ(ComparableType type)
      Constructs a bytecode that compares the top two elements of the stack to check if they are the same.
      IF_CMPNE(ComparableType type)
      Constructs a bytecode that compares the top two elements of the stack to check if they are the same.
      NE(ComparableType type)
      Constructs a bytecode that checks if the top two elements of the stack are not the same.
